      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve the <strong>remaining vegetable stock mix </strong>in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span><strong> boiled water</strong></p><p>Stir in your <strong>tomato paste </strong>and <strong>harissa paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) – this is your <strong>harissa stock</strong></p>",
