    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the beans are starting to colour, add the <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes</strong> and<strong> harissa stock </strong>to the pan</p><p>Cover with the lid and cook for 4-5 min or until the tomatoes have broken down and the sauce has thickened</p>",
